João F. Ferreira is an assistant professor at [IST](https://dei.tecnico.ulisboa.pt), [University of Lisbon](https://www.ulisboa.pt), and a researcher at [INESC-ID](https://inesc-id.pt). His research is on mathematical approaches to software quality, with emphasis on program construction and verification. For more details, see [selected publications](#featured).
